        <tr><td>Gas pressure / regulator referral (plumber-side)</td><td>$120 plus plumber-side $200-600</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Windbreak retrofit (rooftop / exposed patio)</td><td>$400 to $1,200 structural fab</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Coastal sealed-seam annual inspection</td><td>$160 to $240</td></tr>
        <tr><td>LP tank wrap / heating mitigation kit</td><td>$120 to $280 customer purchase</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Multi-component (year 8+ heavy duty coastal)</td><td>$880 to $1,400</td></tr>
